 
 <!DOCTYPE html>
 <html lang="ko">
 <head>
     <meta charset="UTF-8">
     <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
     <title>EMA516_10_SU_0004_s</title>
 
     <!-- 공통 js-->
     <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>
     
     <!-- 공통 css-->
     <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css">
     
     <!-- 개별 -->
    <script src="./../../common_contents/js/ema516_10_su_0004.js"></script>
     <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/css/ema516_07.css">
 
 </head>
 <body>
     <div id="app_wrap" class="ema516_10_su_0004" data-current-page="page_1, page_2, page_3, page_4, page_5, page_6"><!-- 그리기 기능 필요 -->
        <section class="title type2 page-1-title">
            <h2 lang="y" data-head="2">똑같은 삼각형 2개를 이용하여 삼각형의 넓이를 구하는 방법을 알아봅시다.</h2>
        </section>  
         <section class="contents paging_layout">
             <article class="page page_1">
                <section class="title type2">
                </section>
                    <h3 lang="y">초록색으로 표시된 변을 삼각형의 밑변으로 할 때 높이를 보라색으로 그어 보세요.</h3>
                    <div class="input_area">     
                            <div class="flex align_center gap_12 flex_box">
                                <div class="main_area">         
                                    <img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA516_10_SU/05_bg.svg" alt="배경 이미지">
                                    <div class="unit"><span>1 ㎠</span></div>
                                    <div class="diagram"><img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA516_10_SU/05_peace_1.svg" alt="도형 예시 이미지"></div>
                                        <div class="unit"><span>1 ㎠</span></div>
                                        <div class="answer_img">
                                            <img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA516_10_SU/05_exp_img_1.svg" alt="정답 예시 이미지">
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                
                                <div class="canvas_wrap">
                                    <!-- 선을 그릴 캔버스 -->
                                    <canvas
                                        class="draw-area"
                                        id="canvas"
                                        width="603"
                                        height="343"
                                        data-canvas-id="canvas_1"></canvas>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                    </div>
                    <!-- 그리기도구 팝업 -->
                    <div class="draw-tool-wrap" id="dragWrap" data-canvas-id="canvas_1">
                    <div class="draw-tool-wrap-header">
                        <div class="draw-tool-wrap-title" id="dragMe">그리기 도구</div>
                        <div class="close_but add_cursor">
                        <img
                            src="../../common_contents/common/img/tool_drawing/tools_close.svg"
                            alt="ic_cancel" />
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="draw-tool-wrap-body">
                        <div class="tool-row function-item">
                        <button type="button" class="ic_pen active"></button>
                        <button type="button" class="ic_txt"></button>
                        <button type="button" class="ic_eraser"></button>
                        </div>
                        <div class="tool-row function-item">
                        <button type="button" class="ic_triangle"></button>
                        <button type="button" class="ic_square"></button>
                        <button type="button" class="ic_circle"></button>
                        <button type="button" class="ic_polygon"></button>
                        </div>
                        <div class="tool-row function-item">
                        <button type="button" class="ic_line"></button>
                        <button type="button" class="ic_dash"></button>
                        <button type="button" class="ic_draw"></button>
                        <button type="button" class="ic_pull"></button>
                        </div>
                        <div class="tool-row palette-item">
                        <button type="button" class="p_red"></button>
                        <button type="button" class="p_yellow"></button>
                        <button type="button" class="p_green"></button>
                        <button type="button" class="p_blue"></button>
                        <button type="button" class="p_purple"></button>
                        <button type="button" class="p_black active"></button>
                        </div>
                        <div class="tool-row range-item">
                        <input type="range" name="thickness" class="draw-scale-range" />
                        </div>
                        <div class="tool-row range-item">
                        <input type="range" name="opacity" class="draw-trans-range" />
                        </div>
                        <div class="tool-row function-item">
                        <div class="arrow-item">
                            <button type="button" class="ic_undo"></button>
                            <button type="button" class="ic_redo"></button>
                        </div>
                        <button type="button" class="ic_del"></button>
                        </div>

                        <div class="ic_polygon_pop">
                        <span>꼭지점</span>
                        <button type="button" class="ipp_minus"></button>
                        <div>
                            <input type="text" name="ipp_num" id="ipp_num" value="5" readonly="readonly" />
                            <label for="ipp_num">개</label>
                        </div>
                        <button type="button" class="ipp_plus"></button>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    </div>
                    <!-- //그리기도구 팝업 -->
             </article><!-- 1page -->
             
             <article class="page page_2 page2">
                 <h3 lang="y">똑같은 삼각형 2개를 이어 붙여 평행사변형을 만들어 보세요.</h3>
                 <div class="input_area po_absolute"> 
                     <div class="flex align_center gap_12 flex_box">
                         <div class="main_wrap">
                             <div class="main_area">
                                 <img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA516_07_SU/06_005_bg.png" alt="도형 예시 이미지">
                                     <div class="unit"><span>1 ㎠</span></div>
                                    <div class="peace_img peace_orgtriangle"><img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA516_07_SU/07_peace4.png" alt="삼각형 조각 이미지"></div>
                                    <div class="peace_img peace_img1 hidden"><img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA516_07_SU/07_peace1.png" alt="삼각형 조각 이미지"></div>
                                    <div class="peace_img peace_img2 hidden"><img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA516_07_SU/07_peace2.png" alt="삼각형 조각 이미지"></div>
                             </div>
                            <div class="sub_area">
                                <div class="example_box answer_img">
                                    <img class="sample_img" src="../../common_contents/img/EMA516_07_SU/07_peace5.png" alt="정답 예시 이미지" />
                                </div>
                                <div class="drop_area"></div>
                             </div>
                         </div>
                         </div>
                     </div>
             </article><!-- 2page -->
 
             <article class="page page_3">
                 <h3 lang="y">만든 평행사변형의 밑변의 길이와 높이는 각각 삼각형의 무엇과 같나요?</h3>
                 <div class="input_area po_absolute"> 
                     <div class="flex"> 
                         <div class="dorp_box">
                             <div class="top_txt">
                                 <span lang="y">만든 평행사변형의 밑변의 길이는 삼각형의&nbsp;</span>
                             <div class="dropdown_wrap">
                                 <select class="custom_dropdown" data-answer-single="밑변의 길이">
                                 <option value="밑변의 길이" lang="y">밑변의 길이</option>
                                 <option value="높이" lang="y">높이</option></select>
                                 <span lang="y">&nbsp;와 같고,</span>
                             </div>
                     </div>
                     <div class="bottom_txt">
                         <span lang="y">높이는 삼각형의&nbsp;</span>
                         <div class="dropdown_wrap">
                             <select class="custom_dropdown" data-answer-single="높이">
                                 <option value="밑변의 길이" lang="y">밑변의 길이</option>
                                 <option value="높이" lang="y"> 높이</option>
                             </select>
                         <span lang="y">&nbsp;와 같습니다.</span>
                     </div>
             </article><!-- 3page --> 
 
             <article class="page page_4">
                 <h3 lang="y">평행사변형의 넓이를 이용하여 삼각형의 넓이를 구하는 방법을 이야기해 보세요.</h3>
                 <div class="text_area">
                     <div class="input_wrap">
                         <math-field class="textarea"></math-field>
                         <div class="example_box ">
                             <p lang="y"> 
                                삼각형의 넓이는 만든 평행사변형의 넓이의 반이므로 삼각형의 넓이는 밑변의
                                길이와 높이의 곱을 2로 나누어 구합니다</p>
                         </div>
                     </div>
                 </div>
             </article><!-- 4page --> 
             <article class="page page_5">
                 <h3 lang="y">삼각형의 넓이를 구하는 방법을 식으로 나타내어 보세요.</h3> 
                 <div class="input_area po_absolute">
                     <div class="question_box dir_col align_start">
                         <div class="rowArea" style="position: relative;">
                             <div class="line">
                                 <div class="modification2">
                                     <div>
                                         <span lang="y">(삼각형의 넓이)=</span>
                                         <button class="reveal_btn btn_1" data-pair="1">밑변의 길이 </button>
                                         <span>×</span>
                                         <button class="reveal_btn btn_2" data-pair="1">높이</button>
                                         <span>÷</span>
                                         <span>2</span>
                                     </div>
                                 </div>
                             </div>
                         </div>
                     </div>        
             </article><!-- 5page --> 
             <article class="page page_6">
                 <h3 lang="y">식을 이용하여 삼각형의 넓이는 몇 ㎠인지 구해 보세요.</h3>
                 <div class="question_box dir_col align_start">
                 <div class="flex">
                     <span lang="y">식:</span>
                     <div class="input_wrap answer1">
                        <math-field type="number" data-answer-single="8×4÷2" text-align="center"></math-field>
                    </div>
                     <span>=</span>
                     <div class="input_wrap answer2">
                        <math-field type="number" data-answer-single="16" text-align="center"></math-field>
                    </div>
                 </div>
                 <div class="flex">
                     <span lang="y">답:</span>
                     <div class="input_wrap">
                        <math-field type="number" data-answer-single="16" text-align="center"></math-field>
                    </div>
                     <span>㎠</span>
                 </div>
             </div>
             </article><!-- 5page --> 
            <button type="button" class="btn btn_draw"></button>
            <div class="btn_area"> 
                <button class="btnType">입력타입토글</button>
                <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
                <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
                <button class="btnSubmit">확인</button>
                    <button class="btnSubmit" lang="y" data-submit="true">확인</button>
            </div>
         </section>
     </div>
 </body>
 </html>